<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="kr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>계정 만들기</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="none">
            <div class="profile"></div>
            <div class="name"><%= name %>님, 오늘도 파이팅!</div>
        </div>
        <div class="menu"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <div class="box a10">검색부분</div>
        <div class="box a10">북마크</div>
        <div class="box a10">글 쓰러 가는 부분</div>
        <div class="box a50">인기 글 목록 쭉</div>
        <div class="box a50">과목별로 보기 1</div>
        <div class="box a50">과목별로 보기 2</div>
        <div class="box a50">과목별로 보기 3</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

<style>

    div {
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .none {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
    }

    body {
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        flex-direction: column;
        background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);
        position: absolute;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        margin-bottom: 100px;
        overflow: scroll;
    }

    .header {
        display: flex;
        padding: 15px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
        position: sticky;
        top: 0px;
        z-index: 9999;
        justify-content: space-between;
        background-color: rgb(245, 245, 245);
    }

    .profile {
        width: 45px;
        height: 45px;
        border-radius: 100px;
        background-image: url("/images/profile.png");
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: 100%;
        background-position: 5% center;
        margin-right: 12px;
        border: 1px solid gray;
        margin-left: 10px;
        background-color: white;
    }

    .menu {
        width: 35px;
        height: 35px;
        background-image: url("/images/menu.png");
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: 100%;
        margin-right: 10px;
    }

    .name {
        font-size: 19px;
    }

    .content {
        margin-left: 20px;
        margin-right: 20px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .box {
        background-color: white;
        display: flex;
        width: 100%;
        border: 1px solid rgb(230, 230, 230);
        border-radius: 20px;
        margin-top: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .a10 {
        height: 65px;
    }

    .a50 {
        height: 300px;
    }

</style> 